PTorrent — Original Author and Maintainer
==========================================

Cody Michael Allison <the.wandering.god@gmail.com>
  - Concept, architecture, protocol design, and all original source code
  - PtolemySeeder Android APK (Kotlin/Python)
  - PTorrent format specification v1.0
  - Medical literature aggregator (DeriveCancerDrugs corpus)
  - Ainulindale / SMMIP theoretical framework

---

PTorrent is part of the Ptolemy / Ainulindale research project.
The protocol is inspired by BitTorrent (Bram Cohen, 2001/2003) — adapted
for corpus distribution without a tracker, gradient server, or central index.

If you contribute to this project, add your name and email below this line,
along with a brief description of your contribution.

